/**
 * \mainpage Exponential CMS — PHP Class Reference
 *
 * \section intro Introduction
 *
 * This is the complete PHP class reference for <b>Exponential 6.0.13</b>, the
 * open-source enterprise CMS maintained by <a href="https://se7enx.com">7x (se7enxweb)</a>.
 *
 * Source: <a href="https://github.com/se7enxweb/exponential">github.com/se7enxweb/exponential</a>
 *
 * \section browse Browse the Documentation
 *
 * - \ref annotated "Class List" — All documented PHP classes
 * - \ref hierarchy "Class Hierarchy" — Inheritance tree
 * - \ref functions "Class Members" — All class methods and properties
 * - \ref files "File List" — Source files with documentation
 * - \ref globals "File Members" — Global functions and variables
 * - \ref modules "Modules" — Documentation groups
 *
 * \section libs Libraries
 *
 * | Library | Description |
 * |---------|-------------|
 * | \b ezdb | Database abstraction layer (MySQL, MySQLi, PostgreSQL, SQLite) |
 * | \b ezdbschema | Database schema abstraction |
 * | \b ezfile | File and directory utilities |
 * | \b ezi18n | Internationalisation and translation |
 * | \b ezimage | Image handling and conversion |
 * | \b ezlocale | Locale, date, time and number formatting |
 * | \b ezpdf | PDF generation |
 * | \b ezsoap | SOAP client/server |
 * | \b eztemplate | Template engine |
 * | \b ezutils | Miscellaneous utility classes |
 *
 * \section kernel Kernel
 *
 * The \b kernel contains the core CMS classes covering content objects,
 * content classes, datatypes, users, roles, workflows, search, and more.
